<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Founders — Aquiplex</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Meet the founders of Aquiplex — the team behind Aqua AI.">
  <link rel="icon" href="/logo/favicon.ico" sizes="any">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/platform.css">
</head>
<body class="px-page">

  <%- include("partials/nav") %>

  <section class="px-page-hero center">
    <div class="px-container">
      <div class="px-eyebrow">Founders</div>
      <h1>The team behind Aqua.</h1>
      <p>Aquiplex is built by a small team obsessed with one idea: AI that executes, not just answers.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main style="padding-bottom:96px;">
    <div class="px-container">
      <div class="px-founder-grid">

        <div class="px-founder">
          <div class="name">Chhanda Prabal Das</div>
          <div class="role">Co-Founder &amp; Advisor</div>
          <div class="desc">
            The original mind behind Aquiplex. Chhanda is a student and entrepreneur who has worked on multiple early-stage startups, including Uniqence and Acodet. His experience building products from scratch shaped the vision of Aquiplex — an ecosystem focused on execution, not just ideas.
          </div>
          <div class="links">
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/chhanda.pr" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Instagram</a>
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/chhanda-prabal-das-7198a0280" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="px-founder">
          <div class="name">Ananya Prabal Das</div>
          <div class="role">Chief Executive Officer</div>
          <div class="desc">
            Leading the execution of Aquiplex, Ananya manages daily operations and drives the platform's development. He plays a key role in turning ideas into real features — working across the full stack to build and scale Aquiplex, from Aqua's engine to the workspace around it.
          </div>
          <div class="links">
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/ananya.p.r.a" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Instagram</a>
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ananya-prabal-das-024293383" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="px-sec-head center" style="margin:88px auto 0; max-width:640px; text-align:center;">
        <div class="px-eyebrow">Our vision</div>
        <h2>An operating system for intent.</h2>
        <p>Aquiplex is being built as a complete AI system where you can generate content, build projects, and turn ideas into reality — through one intelligence, Aqua, that plans, reasons, and executes. This is just the beginning.</p>
        <div style="display:flex; justify-content:center; gap:12px; margin-top:28px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
          <a href="/aqua" class="px-btn px-btn-primary">Open Aqua</a>
          <a href="/about" class="px-btn px-btn-secondary">About the platform</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <%- include("partials/footer") %>

</body>
</html>
